Steamwebapi

This module provides an OO implementation to access Valve steam web api (https://developer.valvesoftware.com/wiki/Steam_Web_API). 
Simply create an object, in which apikey is an optional parameter to pass, and use the methods defined below to fetch result. 
Default return format would be json, unless specified so. Also check the examples included.

	use Steamwebapi;
	use Data::Dumper;
	
	my $object = Steamwebapi->new();
	my $result = $object->GetAppList();
	print Dumper $result;
	
INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make && make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find detailed documentation for this module with the
perldoc command or try the man command also

    	perldoc Steamwebapi
    	man Steamwebapi

